briefdescription.para: Helper class for accessing Value of object type.

detaileddescription.para: Instance of this helper class is obtained by GenericValue::GetObject(). In addition to all APIs for array type, it provides range-based for loop if CEREAL_RAPIDJSON_HAS_CXX11_RANGE_FOR=1.
